OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start across England and
OL,6,FWales as a band of rain, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, moves southeastwards. Sunshine
OL,8,Fand showers across Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fand Scotland, with this spreading to
OL,10,Fmost areas by the end of the day. Cool
OL,11,Fand breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMostly dry this evening
OL,14,Facross England and Wales, but frequent
OL,15,Fshowers for Northern Ireland and
OL,16,FScotland. These spreading to most
OL,17,Fareas overnight. Turning rather chilly
OL,18,Funder the clearest skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
